e-mail: promed@usa.healthnet.org
[The decision to re-introduce smallpox vaccination in Central Africa is a
tricky issue, due to the high prevalence of HIV infection in some areas. It
is possible that smallpox vaccination would inflict more damage than the
current monkeypox outbreak. I wouldn't like to be involved in this decision.
- LJdaS
[On the other hand, one must try to prevent a real disease and not be swayed
by the possibility of another disease. - Mod.CHC.
